source ~/.bashrc # THIS IS A VERY IMPORTANT COMMAND.YOU MAY HAVE THE BEST/LATEST SOFTWARE, BUT IF UNIX DOESNT KNOW WHERE TO LOOK FOR THE SOFTWARE..IT IS AS BAD AS NOT THERE!!!
